793
00:57:58,708 --> 00:58:00,958
I'm Wan Greeney from W. Kityont.

794
00:58:02,125 --> 00:58:03,583
I'm Suk Bravery from P. Pratad.

795
00:58:13,666 --> 00:58:16,125
I'm Menn Pointy

796
00:58:17,208 --> 00:58:18,500
from P. Pratheep.

797
