Did you spill it all over yourself?

962
01:09:54,041 --> 01:09:56,250
Don't just stare, dear.

963
01:09:56,333 --> 01:09:57,333
Look.

964
01:09:58,416 --> 01:10:02,041
Will you please
fill out the form right here?

965
